{"tid":2349441,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"幾歲開始feel 到自己通唔到頂","createTime":"2021-01-01T14:31:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T06:54:19.000Z","uid":210067,"like":25,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ca4f87f1c636239061d917699640f4e5e986d106","tid":2349441,"uid":210067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:31:47.000Z","msg":"尋晚倒數去咗倒數同睇日出，只不過通一晚頂，已經feel 到胸口好唔舒服，每一刻都好辛苦。就算之前溫書，通一晚，都開始頂唔順。<br />\n<br />\n22歲搞到咁，是否悲哀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好就好在訓一覺就會好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a83365290b9a261071df1c2d98b6b41f2f51321","tid":2349441,"uid":86673,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:32:21.000Z","msg":"出世第一日 成日都要瞓"},{"pid":"e9c77c777520c664d7b529601ed7b7a7cdc02542","tid":2349441,"uid":210067,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a83365290b9a261071df1c2d98b6b41f2f51321","tid":2349441,"uid":86673,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:32:21.000Z","msg":"出世第一日 成日都要瞓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:38:41.000Z","msg":"我都係，經常訓十二個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a021b368f80d7248154024eb9a9cad44b9847dbf","tid":2349441,"uid":219722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:39:22.000Z","msg":"三十"},{"pid":"37b7ec201b5d18a89762f3f4d659c2db4a102ab5","tid":2349441,"uid":194281,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:39:43.000Z","msg":"通頂就爆瘡<br />\n依家最遲1點訓"},{"pid":"b41d408d9c47b8d9037d507fcc8605b958b827e4","tid":2349441,"uid":128308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:00:03.000Z","msg":"28"},{"pid":"2e9aee1afbabee2c7f24b060636199fb048571cc","tid":2349441,"uid":121911,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:02:36.000Z","msg":"25歲後 開始打一次波要起碼3日復原<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a4306ce6047d81322d8ae581b09c3a7ab749f3","tid":2349441,"uid":226849,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ca4f87f1c636239061d917699640f4e5e986d106","tid":2349441,"uid":210067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:31:47.000Z","msg":"尋晚倒數去咗倒數同睇日出，只不過通一晚頂，已經feel 到胸口好唔舒服，每一刻都好辛苦。就算之前溫書，通一晚，都開始頂唔順。<br />\n<br />\n22歲搞到咁，是否悲哀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好就好在訓一覺就會好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:06:24.000Z","msg":"正常 我21歲到而家都未試過&amp;唔夠膽通頂"},{"pid":"32f408fcb84bd82b35cfe11c62041180b4b2a945","tid":2349441,"uid":223084,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:11:38.000Z","msg":"冇通宵習慣<br />\n突然有一晚通頂會辛苦到想死"},{"pid":"d5f7011b13871fad0f4cad28696c06aa4bdd94c2","tid":2349441,"uid":141237,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:44:53.000Z","msg":"身體質素既嘢係遺傳，唔係你搞成點就可以勁d。當然後天做既嘢有一定程度影響。<br />\n<br />\nbtw，讀大學既時候已經feel到自己係唔捱得夜，一去到3點4點，成個人諗唔到嘢，半喪屍狀態，個腦load出黎既嘢極度劣質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以自此唔會選擇捱夜趕嘢，情願收拾好心情訓好d，早少少起身睇下點，不過訓唔夠都係無乜用，靠彩數，不過個人認為睡眠質素係最重要，俾你訓20個鐘訓得唔好都無撚用。"},{"pid":"3854eebba041790889637106757ccedfa5c351ca","tid":2349441,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:59:30.000Z","msg":"以前可以通完頂直落連踩多日<br />\n而家通一次要訓返兩日，仲成日見暈同心跳快到傻咗"},{"pid":"98e8c30687b45ed40a3687447eb353a788375e15","tid":2349441,"uid":35112,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T18:38:38.000Z","msg":"25,26到"},{"pid":"d495ef109a7a7c5bc718cd586e90266b353842cc","tid":2349441,"uid":371298,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T18:39:22.000Z","msg":"Year 2"},{"pid":"9b5b67400cf35e5b063444404cb02ca230f08390","tid":2349441,"uid":181549,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T18:40:34.000Z","msg":"大學畢業後無試過因為玩/追劇通頂 除左返工"},{"pid":"743d892a8ef31248a0a34d032e5dfc76f1091fe8","tid":2349441,"uid":16087,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47a4306ce6047d81322d8ae581b09c3a7ab749f3","tid":2349441,"uid":226849,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ca4f87f1c636239061d917699640f4e5e986d106","tid":2349441,"uid":210067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:31:47.000Z","msg":"尋晚倒數去咗倒數同睇日出，只不過通一晚頂，已經feel 到胸口好唔舒服，每一刻都好辛苦。就算之前溫書，通一晚，都開始頂唔順。<br />\n<br />\n22歲搞到咁，是否悲哀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好就好在訓一覺就會好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T16:06:24.000Z","msg":"正常 我21歲到而家都未試過&amp;唔夠膽通頂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T18:42:43.000Z","msg":"中學試過<br />\n根本唔想自己去有呢種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以中學之後都冇通頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定要訓覺,就算5點先訓都要訓一訓"},{"pid":"be02829bb3c6ebfc4bac553502799a6be4c9e69e","tid":2349441,"uid":121546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T04:12:25.000Z","msg":"我調返轉<br />\n通頂同夜訓冇問題<br />\n早起身會成個人散晒 冇胃口食野"},{"pid":"33d2ea657e9856ecf22bfd74ed358932faa72e46","tid":2349441,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T04:14:54.000Z","msg":"Year4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗住夜晚一兩點打埋篇論文<br />\n點知精神差到連平時用開啲字都唔記得曬點串<br />\n但完全唔覺眼瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a18ccda49bd9bd40a9560e578491a4328f34058","tid":2349441,"uid":1239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T04:38:56.000Z","msg":"25 咁上下<br />\n寧願早啲瞓 凌晨醒好過通頂<br />\n不過以前讀書都係臨考前好早瞓 凌晨三四點起身溫返重點<br />\nso far 冇肥過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n通頂我都試過幾個月 應該係話日夜時間倒轉 日頭瞓覺 夜晚就隨意<br />\n但身體差咗好多"},{"pid":"8339f6d2d6c2e44f43aeac35e785b4dcde3ab042","tid":2349441,"uid":17546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T06:52:04.000Z","msg":"返工關係一個月起碼有8日係返通宵更  <br />\n返左6年 近2年開始覺得唔係幾頂到<br />\n依家28"},{"pid":"e56458d92a0e86fa276bc919611c03a8da274d94","tid":2349441,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T06:54:19.000Z","msg":"以前開夜有ot 係咁做 <br />\n依家廿中出親街都話攰"}]}